@name Qwen3VL_Abliterated:30B-A3B-Instruct-Q4
@base Huihui-Qwen3-VL-30B-A3B-Instruct-abliterated-GGUF_Q4
@thinking-off

# Vision-only model: one profile, no thinking training. "Instruct" in the
# name signals that to users, and @thinking-off enforces it (the old config
# only claimed thinking-off in a comment but parsed as thinking=True).
# Sampling: official Qwen3-VL — temp 0.7, top-p 0.8, presence 1.5
# (mradermacher/huihui docs), not the abliterated Qwen3.6 defaults.

temperature 0.7
top-p 0.8
top-k 20
min-p 0.0
presence-penalty 1.5
repetition-penalty 1.0
